## Validation Tools

Runnable scripts in `.claude/tools/`:

```bash
# After engine changes
bash .claude/tools/validate-rust.sh check

# After frontend changes (lint + tsc + vitest)
bash .claude/tools/validate-frontend.sh quick

# After MCP changes (manifest sync + tests)
bash .claude/tools/validate-mcp.sh full

# Test inventory and coverage
bash .claude/tools/validate-tests.sh coverage

# Documentation integrity
bash .claude/tools/validate-docs.sh

# DX audit (cross-IDE consistency, doc freshness)
bash .claude/tools/dx-audit.sh

# Run everything
bash .claude/tools/validate-all.sh
```

